casebody.head_matter:
REPUBLIC OF SUDAN, et al., Petitioners,
v.
James OWENS, et al.
No. 17-1236.
Supreme Court of the United States.
May 26, 2020
Motion of Former U.S. Ambassadors for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted.
Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied. Justice Kavanaugh took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.
